    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Adventurer's Armory pg. 19</em><br/><strong>Price</strong> 8 sp; <strong>Weight</strong> 2 lbs.<br/><strong>Category</strong> Tools</p><h2 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\" title=\"PFS Legal\"/>Description</h2><p>Consisting of a small wooden frame with inward-pointing barbed spikes, this trap is placed in a shallow pit just deep enough for a Medium-sized character's lower leg. When someone steps in the square, the boot catches and holds her leg. The target takes damage if she tries to move or if a Disable Device attempt to free her fails by 5 or more.<br/><br/><strong>Trespasser 's Boot - CR 1/2</strong><br/><strong>Type</strong> mechanical; <strong>Perception</strong> DC 20; <strong>Disable Device</strong> DC 20<br/><strong>Trigger</strong> location; <strong>Reset</strong> manual<br/><strong>Effect</strong> pit spikes (Atk +10 melee, 2d4); spikes hold the target in place; the trap can be escaped with a DC 20 Disable Device check, DC 20 Escape Artist check, or DC 24 Strength check</p>",
